{"tid":2391524,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"海賊王 1003 情報（下周不休刊）","createTime":"2021-02-02T09:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T11:42:57.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"80bd4c90ab6f37ed6cea6e89adbc6552be3c7e94","tid":2391524,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:27:14.000Z","msg":"1003話標題 盤上之夜<br />\n情報師：這盤上（棋盤）不止表示了屋頂的情形，還代表鬼島決戰的形態。 （注：首次更新的情報常常就是這樣的模糊風格，等後面補充了。）<br />\n下週不休刊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dk6YPow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDk6YPow.jpg&h=802d893e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有最新消息，會置頂補充<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題目係咁，尾田唔通用棋局表達今次戰爭，點都好，即係開始準備講其他人情況<br />\n（特別係山治）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不死鳥點一抽二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n山治幫手啦屌<br />\n<br />\n按照慣例，講完其他人，應該就大媽凱多回憶，最後BOSS收皮"},{"pid":"2e5220ddb55bd888988660b5fe1b50ae140c4cfd","tid":2391524,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"山治唔該生生性性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bd09d65ce13ce9c23b09a7b0ef782b5f1b064c","tid":2391524,"uid":312193,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jxsd8nr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxsd8nr.gif&h=fd3c0fba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0UKuT1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0UKuT1.gif&h=ea5ee1e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WVRM4c.png&h=ec331784&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96967f41a077b832f34f583cff4ffe1004033f2a","tid":2391524,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"咩情報嚟<img src=\"/assets/f